1
00:01:21,050 --> 00:01:26,760
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,539 --> 00:01:29,470
[Episode 14]

3
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,820
If you had even a shred of sense,

4
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:33,960
you'd never

5
00:01:34,430 --> 00:01:37,150
bring up divorce again.

6
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,710
I will never agree to it.

7
00:01:41,950 --> 00:01:43,070
Gu Dezhao!

8
00:01:58,110 --> 00:01:59,310
I just want to ask you.

9
00:02:00,290 --> 00:02:02,750
Back then,
when you insisted on marrying me,

10
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:05,950
was it out of genuine love for me,

11
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,120
or

12
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,600
merely for the support of the Ji family?

13
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:14,000
You're acting like this again.

14
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:15,820
Ji Han.

15
00:02:16,430 --> 00:02:18,120
It's been so many years.

16
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,870
Why are you still asking this?

17
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:31,590
My Lady.

18
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:33,030
What did

19
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,870
the Master say?

20
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,310
These gardenias smell so good.

21
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:06,360
Madam,

22
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:08,030
they haven't even bloomed yet.

23
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:09,560
That's probably magnolia.

24
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:20,740
[Misty Waters, Gentle Waves]

25
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,840
Madam.

26
00:03:25,090 --> 00:03:25,870
Madam,

27
00:03:26,430 --> 00:03:27,910
why did you come out?

28
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,500
I wanted to get some fresh air.

29
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,660
I brought you black chicken soup,

30
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,940
with codonopsis and goji berries added,

31
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:38,030
just right for your condition.

32
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,150
Okay.

33
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:41,520
Miss Gu is so filial.

34
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:43,000
No wonder last night,

35
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,680
Madam kept calling out for Zhao.

36
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,410
[Misty Waters, Gentle Waves]

37
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,670
You are so pretty.

38
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:19,300
You are pretty too.

39
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,020
You're just flattering me again.

40
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,120
I'm not flattering you.

41
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,070
If you weren't pretty,

42
00:04:27,630 --> 00:04:29,760
how could I end up looking good myself?

43
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:33,270
I can never win an argument with you.

44
00:04:36,870 --> 00:04:37,630
It's been a while

45
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:38,900
since I last saw Rong.

46
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:41,040
He is so playful.

47
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:43,300
I am playful?

48
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,400
I came yesterday afternoon,

49
00:04:45,409 --> 00:04:46,480
yesterday evening,

50
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,840
and this morning as well.

51
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,300
How is it that I am playful?

52
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:51,300
You always falsely accuse me.

53
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,240
When he came this morning,

54
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,200
you were still asleep,

55
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,390
so we didn't wake you.

56
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:55,950
Listen.

57
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,520
Good thing I have a witness.

58
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:58,720
All right, all right.

59
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,870
My bad.

60
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:03,600
It's getting windy. Let's go back inside.

61
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,120
Okay.

62
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:06,590
Mother, let me help you.

63
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,220
Be careful.

64
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:18,000
It is said that
there was once a tofu beauty,

65
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,310
who was beautiful but never smiled.

66
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,720
Two idle men

67
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,240
made a bet.

68
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:22,950
The first said,

69
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,120
"If you can make her laugh

70
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,260
with just one word,

71
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:26,830
I'll give you five taels of silver."

72
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:27,890
The second agreed,

73
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,830
and they went

74
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,160
to find the tofu beauty.

75
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,270
They saw the woman standing at the door,

76
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:33,360
with a dog nearby.

77
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,040
The second man quickly stepped forward,

78
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,040
fell to his knees

79
00:05:36,310 --> 00:05:37,370
in front of the dog,

80
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,880
and called out "Father."

81
00:05:40,860 --> 00:05:41,850
The woman burst out laughing,

82
00:05:41,850 --> 00:05:43,090
just like you.

83
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,530
Then the first man said,

84
00:05:44,530 --> 00:05:45,800
"If you can make her curse

85
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,900
with one word,

86
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,950
I'll give you another five taels."

87
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,510
So the second man immediately looked up

88
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:51,750
and shouted at her,

89
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,480
"Mother!"

90
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:55,870
How is it?

91
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,920
I heard it from someone outside.

92
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,430
It's been a tiring day.

93
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:02,000
Go back and rest.

94
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:05,490
You should rest early too.

95
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:07,630
I'll come pay my respects tomorrow.

96
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:08,750
I'll come too.

97
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,680
Zhao.

98
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:31,360
You have been back for a few days.

99
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,830
Could you

100
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,310
call me "Mother"?

101
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,800
It's fine.

102
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,360
It's fine.

103
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,120
Go get some rest.

104
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,870
Go.

105
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,480
She just

106
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,120
wants you to call her "Mother."

107
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,250
Why won't you say it?

108
00:07:49,470 --> 00:07:51,870
You wouldn't understand
even if I told you.

109
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,620
Let me ask you instead.

110
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:54,920
Have you run into something

111
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,310
these past few days?

112
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,520
What?

113
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,800
I'm in the manor every day

114
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,560
and never go out.

115
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:02,220
What trouble could I run into?

116
00:08:02,870 --> 00:08:03,720
It's getting late.

117
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,650
Go back and rest.

118
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:16,040
Ms. Zhao.

119
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,620
Thank you for your hard work
all these years.

120
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:23,120
What are you talking about, Madam?

121
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,480
As long as I can take care of you,

122
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,630
I don't find it hard.

123
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,390
Madam, don't take

124
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:39,990
the Master's words to heart.

125
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,480
You have Rong

126
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:42,840
and Zhao here,

127
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:44,870
and Old Madam to support you.

128
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,560
As long as you can take things in stride,

129
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,240
you can live a good life.

130
00:08:58,910 --> 00:08:59,390
Come.

131
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,360
My mother has come to take me home!

132
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:33,120
[Rising Clouds and Radiant Skies]

133
00:10:31,910 --> 00:10:33,770
My mother has come to take me home!

134
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,750
Mother!

135
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:38,750
Mother?

136
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:50,470
Mother.

137
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:02,840
My Lady.

138
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,550
What's wrong?

139
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,790
My Lady.

140
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,200
Madam... she...

141
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:32,960
Zhao.

142
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:52,190
Madam.

143
00:12:55,140 --> 00:12:56,540
What did you just call me?

144
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:13,320
Did you get hurt anywhere?

145
00:13:18,250 --> 00:13:20,190
I am so sorry.

146
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,320
In my whole life,

147
00:13:23,900 --> 00:13:26,050
the person I've felt most sorry for

148
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,840
is my daughter—

149
00:13:29,430 --> 00:13:30,620
you.

150
00:13:53,730 --> 00:13:55,980
You've been back for a few days now.

151
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,550
Could you

152
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:01,870
call me "Mother"?

153
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,150
It's fine.

154
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:12,550
It's fine.

155
00:14:25,410 --> 00:14:26,550
Miss Gu.

156
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,720
Madam...

157
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:38,910
After Rong and I

158
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:39,840
left last night,

159
00:14:41,770 --> 00:14:43,540
did anything happen?

160
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,640
Madam was crying all night.

161
00:14:47,610 --> 00:14:49,650
You don't know, Miss Gu.

162
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:51,320
Over the years,

163
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:53,870
Master has grown distant from Madam.

164
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:56,440
She has suffered in silence,

165
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:58,130
unable to speak her pain,

166
00:14:59,020 --> 00:15:01,350
and it has worn her down
until she fell ill.

167
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:04,030
Now, with Yuping suddenly appearing,

168
00:15:04,030 --> 00:15:06,030
Master refuses to
listen to any explanation

169
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:06,790
and is convinced

170
00:15:06,790 --> 00:15:08,960
that Madam harmed Mrs. Yun.

171
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:12,290
Madam has nowhere to defend herself.

172
00:15:12,630 --> 00:15:15,150
She even considered divorcing Master.

173
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,050
Divorce?

174
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:21,000
I think

175
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:23,960
instead of
enduring things here in the Gu family,

176
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:26,200
you might as well separate from Master

177
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,600
and go back to Tongzhou.

178
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:29,930
We could just live our own lives well.

179
00:15:30,490 --> 00:15:31,620
You mean...

180
00:15:33,310 --> 00:15:35,760
you want me to divorce your father?

181
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,110
No, no.

182
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,360
Absolutely not.

183
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:45,850
The divorce papers
have already been written,

184
00:15:46,030 --> 00:15:47,680
but Master refuses to agree.

185
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:48,600
He even came yesterday

186
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,360
and had a fight with Madam.

187
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:51,630
Miss Gu.

188
00:15:51,970 --> 00:15:54,150
Master must have said something

189
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:57,300
that made Madam feel
she couldn't live anymore.

190
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:59,070
Miss Gu.

191
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:01,950
Madam is truly wronged.

192
00:16:05,670 --> 00:16:06,960
His courtyard

193
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:09,670
[Hall of Virtue and Splendor]

194
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,480
is near Baoxiang Temple.

195
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:09,350
Moreover,

196
00:16:09,790 --> 00:16:11,670
it's elegant and quiet,

197
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:14,090
with beautiful scenery all around.

198
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:16,610
It's perfect for you to recover there.

199
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,720
Great.

200
00:16:20,270 --> 00:16:20,840
Then,

201
00:16:21,070 --> 00:16:22,760
let's set out in two days.

202
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,440
You are so pretty.

203
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,000
Mother!

204
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,080
Mother!

205
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,240
Mother!

206
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:58,270
Mother!

207
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,840
Han.

208
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,420
How could this happen?

209
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:06,550
Mother.

210
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,740
How could this happen?

211
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,480
Gu Dezhao!

212
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:13,900
I'll kill you!

213
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:14,869
My Lady!

214
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:16,440
I'll kill you!

215
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,319
Miss Gu!

216
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:18,510
Zhao!

217
00:17:18,510 --> 00:17:20,440
You killed my mother!

218
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:23,140
Let me go!

219
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:24,180
My Lady.

220
00:17:24,910 --> 00:17:26,660
I'll kill you!

221
00:17:26,930 --> 00:17:28,690
I'll kill you!

222
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:30,830
Let me go!

223
00:17:31,550 --> 00:17:33,240
Let me go!

224
00:17:34,350 --> 00:17:35,400
Let me go.

225
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:43,040
[Gu Mansion] [Memorial]

226
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:46,360
[Enduring Family Legacy] [Memorial]

227
00:17:46,380 --> 00:17:47,330
[The Ji family, blessed by Heaven's
Mandate, prospers through generations]

228
00:17:47,350 --> 00:17:48,610
[The coffin of the Eldest Daughter,
Madam Han, of gentle and proper conduct]

229
00:17:51,090 --> 00:17:53,550
[Memorial]

230
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,480
Mother.

231
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:00,200
Mother.

232
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:05,200
Mother.

233
00:18:15,510 --> 00:18:17,200
Old Madam Ji,

234
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,680
and Mr. Ji have arrived.

235
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:50,960
Han.

236
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,350
I am here.

237
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:09,070
I will take you home.

238
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,880
Why didn't you ever tell me

239
00:19:23,650 --> 00:19:26,080
what was weighing on your heart?

240
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,480
You were so willful,

241
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:32,550
leaving me, as a parent,

242
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,900
to see my child

243
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:40,190
die before me.

244
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,350
Mother.

245
00:19:55,020 --> 00:19:56,780
Where is Gu Dezhao?

246
00:19:58,310 --> 00:19:59,920
Where is he?

247
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:18,440
Mother.

248
00:20:27,370 --> 00:20:29,660
How did my Han die?

249
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,350
Tell me.

250
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:43,300
How did my Han die?

251
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:48,680
You heartless bastard.

252
00:20:49,930 --> 00:20:51,680
Get up!

253
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:54,120
Give my Han back!

254
00:20:54,150 --> 00:20:56,510
Give me back her life!

255
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:57,310
Grandmother.

256
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,150
Song Miaohua,

257
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:10,640
come out!

258
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:12,250
Old Madam!

259
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:13,790
With Mother's passing,

260
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:15,840
our whole family is devastated.

261
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:17,280
But this matter

262
00:21:17,300 --> 00:21:19,200
really has nothing to do
with my birth mother.

263
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:21,150
It has nothing to do with her?

264
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:23,830
It's true.

265
00:21:24,900 --> 00:21:27,770
Like mother, like daughter.

266
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:31,240
-Get up!
-Mother!

267
00:21:33,270 --> 00:21:35,070
Yun Xiang?

268
00:21:36,070 --> 00:21:37,730
Yuping?

269
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,530
You and your daughter

270
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:41,500
schemed to

271
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:43,920
framed Han

272
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:46,240
with baseless accusations

273
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:49,360
and drove her

274
00:21:49,390 --> 00:21:51,110
to her death!

275
00:21:51,130 --> 00:21:51,650
Mother!

276
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:54,230
Neither my birth mother nor I

277
00:21:54,230 --> 00:21:55,030
ever meant to

278
00:21:55,050 --> 00:21:56,510
drive Mother to her death.

279
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:58,560
None of us expected that

280
00:21:58,660 --> 00:21:59,970
she would take her own life.

281
00:21:59,970 --> 00:22:00,660
Shut up!

282
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,470
You still dare argue back?

283
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:08,760
Do you think I can't punish you?

284
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,640
Guards!

285
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:12,080
Wait, Old Madam!

286
00:22:13,330 --> 00:22:15,140
Lan is just young and ignorant.

287
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:17,310
She just spoke nonsense
in a moment of panic.

288
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:19,040
Please forgive her, Old Madam.

289
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,450
Yuping

290
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,370
was brought in by me.

291
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:24,150
It has nothing to do with Lan.

292
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:25,510
Today's disaster

293
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:28,170
is entirely my fault.

294
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:31,480
I know my sins are unforgivable.

295
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:35,850
Whatever punishment you choose—
beating, killing,

296
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,610
or selling me off—I will accept it.

297
00:22:47,560 --> 00:22:48,540
It's not like that.

298
00:22:48,540 --> 00:22:49,400
-Mother.
-Lan!

299
00:22:54,270 --> 00:22:55,920
I beg you to see the truth, Old Madam.

300
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,650
This is about past grievances.

301
00:22:57,790 --> 00:22:59,030
Lan is just a child.

302
00:22:59,030 --> 00:23:00,690
What could she possibly know?

303
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,660
Whatever mistakes were made,

304
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:05,160
they are all my fault.

305
00:23:06,270 --> 00:23:08,100
I beg you to punish me, Old Madam.

306
00:23:09,550 --> 00:23:11,010
I will have no complaints.

307
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:12,750
Alright.

308
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:16,480
You asked for this.

309
00:23:17,790 --> 00:23:18,880
Luo Yongping.

310
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,310
Yes, Old Madam.

311
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:23,390
Concubine Song

312
00:23:24,110 --> 00:23:26,350
has served Madam Ji respectfully.

313
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:30,390
Unable to bear Madam Ji's passing,

314
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,200
she has requested

315
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,440
to keep vigil for Madam Ji.

316
00:23:35,070 --> 00:23:36,510
From tomorrow,

317
00:23:37,190 --> 00:23:40,120
she will be sent to
the Ji family's ancestral temple.

318
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:42,300
and shall not leave

319
00:23:43,510 --> 00:23:45,000
until death.

320
00:23:55,830 --> 00:23:56,830
I, Song Miaohua,

321
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,820
thank you, Old Madam.

322
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:15,440
Mother!

323
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:16,480
Mother.

324
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:18,960
Lan.

325
00:24:19,390 --> 00:24:20,740
I'm sorry.

326
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:23,030
I won't be by your side anymore.

327
00:24:23,030 --> 00:24:24,560
Take good care of yourself.

328
00:24:24,860 --> 00:24:26,120
Don't throw tantrums.

329
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:27,030
Mother!

330
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:28,720
Mother!

331
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,680
It shouldn't be like this.

332
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:34,200
It shouldn't be like this.

333
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,270
Father! Father!

334
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:38,880
Father, please save my mother.

335
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:39,750
Father!

336
00:24:40,130 --> 00:24:41,510
-I can't save her.
-Father.

337
00:24:41,510 --> 00:24:42,520
I beg you.

338
00:24:42,540 --> 00:24:44,290
It's all karma.

339
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,400
What are you waiting for?

340
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:48,400
Drag this wretch away!

341
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:48,960
Yes.

342
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:51,480
Lan!

343
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:52,110
Lan!

344
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:53,310
Mother! Mother!

345
00:24:53,310 --> 00:24:53,920
Lan.

346
00:24:55,350 --> 00:24:56,990
Never be like me

347
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,640
and become a concubine.

348
00:24:59,310 --> 00:25:00,840
-Remember what I said.
-Go.

349
00:25:01,030 --> 00:25:01,830
Remember.

350
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:03,400
Better to be a poor man's wife

351
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:03,960
-Hurry up.
-Mother!

352
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:06,200
than a rich man's concubine.

353
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:07,310
Mother!

354
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:45,310
Mother!

355
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:54,720
Zhao.

356
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:58,000
My poor...

357
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:00,380
-Grandmother!
-Grandmother!

358
00:26:00,380 --> 00:26:00,900
Grandmother!

359
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:01,550
-Old Madam.
-Grandmother.

360
00:26:01,550 --> 00:26:02,680
-Grandmother.
-Go.

361
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:04,510
Quick, get a physician.

362
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,920
With this modification,

363
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,530
it becomes easier to conceal

364
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:12,880
and harder to detect.

365
00:26:13,110 --> 00:26:14,310
But the drawback is that

366
00:26:14,310 --> 00:26:15,790
it can only hold a few needles

367
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:16,990
and has a short range.

368
00:26:17,110 --> 00:26:17,720
This single advantage

369
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:19,160
of being hard to detect

370
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,000
outweighs everything else.

371
00:26:22,510 --> 00:26:24,370
What are you tinkering with here?

372
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:26,550
My Lady.

373
00:26:26,920 --> 00:26:27,650
Master Xiao.

374
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:44,750
Hey.

375
00:26:47,460 --> 00:26:48,560
Ignoring me?

376
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:51,790
Are you holding a grudge against me?

377
00:26:52,800 --> 00:26:53,470
Fine.

378
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:56,350
I was going to ask

379
00:26:56,410 --> 00:26:57,720
if you wanted to go

380
00:26:57,750 --> 00:26:59,010
to Madam Ji's funeral.

381
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:00,790
Since you don't care,

382
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:01,510
never mind then.

383
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:02,110
Come back.

384
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,160
Madam Ji?

385
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,330
You mean Zhao's mother?

386
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:09,640
She died yesterday morning.

387
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:10,070
She...

388
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:12,160
Although she was seriously ill,

389
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:13,110
it wasn't fatal.

390
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:15,400
How could she have suddenly passed away?

391
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,350
I really don't know

392
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:17,510
the exact reason.

393
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,590
There were no signs at all.

394
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:21,390
She was just gone all of a sudden.

395
00:27:22,010 --> 00:27:23,160
Your brother-in-law and Xian

396
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,960
have already been to that manor.

397
00:27:25,590 --> 00:27:27,310
Since I have Hui with me,

398
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,640
Old Madam said

399
00:27:28,750 --> 00:27:30,280
my attendance is optional.

400
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,480
If you want to go,

401
00:27:31,610 --> 00:27:32,480
I'll talk to Father

402
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:33,670
and lift your restriction,

403
00:27:33,670 --> 00:27:35,330
and take you with me tomorrow.

404
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:38,510
Why are you being so nice all of a sudden?

405
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:40,920
I pity you.

406
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:43,880
Anyway, Zhao's mother has passed away,

407
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:45,480
Zhao must observe three years of mourning

408
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:46,680
and cannot marry.

409
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:50,160
Then I have nothing left to worry about.

410
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:29,110
My Lady.

411
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:39,350
It's dawn.

412
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:42,200
Why don't you rest a little longer?

413
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,020
Anyway,

414
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:45,440
no one will be coming
to offer condolences now.

415
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:46,440
I'm fine.

416
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,840
Where are the two of them?

417
00:28:56,310 --> 00:28:58,440
They probably went somewhere to rest.

418
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,590
You stay here.

419
00:29:04,320 --> 00:29:06,190
I'm going to see Grandmother.

420
00:29:44,550 --> 00:29:45,960
The physician added some calming medicine

421
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:47,440
to the prescription.

422
00:29:47,920 --> 00:29:48,680
Last night,

423
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:50,750
she finally slept soundly.

424
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:54,550
Otherwise, she would have woken up
several times every night.

425
00:29:54,550 --> 00:29:56,400
She is getting old after all.

426
00:29:56,750 --> 00:29:59,000
It is truly worrisome.

427
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,510
Grandmother said yesterday,

428
00:30:05,710 --> 00:30:09,840
[The Fragrant Brocade Pavilion]

429
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:08,270
in accordance with Aunt's final wishes,

430
00:30:08,270 --> 00:30:10,640
she will be taken back
to Tongzhou for burial.

431
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,370
She plans to go back the morning

432
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:14,410
the day after tomorrow to prepare.

433
00:30:14,870 --> 00:30:16,800
I'm worried her body won't hold up.

434
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:18,960
Please try your best

435
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,220
to persuade her for me.

436
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:22,830
You know

437
00:30:22,830 --> 00:30:24,160
Grandmother's temper.

438
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,400
She can't be persuaded at all.

439
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:26,160
Besides,

440
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,250
it's good for her to go back.

441
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:29,530
Staying here

442
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:32,000
will only make her even more upset.

443
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:35,160
Okay.

444
00:30:36,930 --> 00:30:38,200
Then take good care of her

445
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,070
on the way.

446
00:30:39,550 --> 00:30:40,440
Rest assured.

447
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:41,480
I've arranged everything

448
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:42,640
for Grandmother.

449
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:43,590
Moreover,

450
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,350
Grandmother told me

451
00:30:45,350 --> 00:30:46,880
to stay and take care of you.

452
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:48,000
I'm fine.

453
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:49,960
I also want to stay here with you.

454
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,330
-I really…
-Be good.

455
00:31:00,330 --> 00:31:05,500
[The Fragrant Brocade Pavilion]

456
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:08,230
[Chen Mansion]

457
00:31:07,070 --> 00:31:07,870
Third Master.

458
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,310
The Gu household is in
complete chaos right now.

459
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:10,710
[Reflect constantly, stay disciplined;
cultivate virtue and the heart]

460
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:11,130
I had someone ask around.

461
00:31:11,130 --> 00:31:12,680
There are all kinds of rumors.

462
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,960
Some say she died of illness.

463
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,000
Some say she was angered to death

464
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,060
by that concubine.

465
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:17,570
And some even say

466
00:31:17,830 --> 00:31:19,030
she took her own life.

467
00:31:20,550 --> 00:31:22,240
Have someone investigate carefully

468
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,480
what really happened.

469
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:24,350
It's best to ask

470
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:25,830
people close to her directly.

471
00:31:25,830 --> 00:31:26,240
Yes.

472
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,160
The expenses

473
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:44,920
for the carriage and the tea
were recorded incorrectly.

474
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,050
Recalculate them

475
00:31:46,310 --> 00:31:47,840
and come back for the money.

476
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:48,680
Yes.

477
00:31:51,330 --> 00:31:52,000
Next.

478
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:58,350
Stop.

479
00:31:59,410 --> 00:32:00,870
You haven't answered yet.

480
00:32:01,070 --> 00:32:02,200
Why are you leaving?

481
00:32:04,570 --> 00:32:05,370
My Lady.

482
00:32:05,510 --> 00:32:06,920
I've come to withdraw

483
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:09,070
the donation money for the temple.

484
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:11,070
I'm worried the accounts aren't correct,

485
00:32:11,070 --> 00:32:12,670
so I plan to recalculate them

486
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:13,830
before coming back to you.

487
00:32:13,830 --> 00:32:15,360
Bring me your account book.

488
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,880
You're not miscalculating.

489
00:32:39,270 --> 00:32:41,400
You've calculated it far too clearly,

490
00:32:43,350 --> 00:32:44,350
even counting

491
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:45,810
your own ritual expenses.

492
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:48,490
I'm not good at calculations.

493
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:50,080
Please forgive me, My Lady.

494
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:51,810
Not good at calculations?

495
00:32:52,510 --> 00:32:53,650
You are too modest.

496
00:32:54,750 --> 00:32:56,010
Look at your accounts.

497
00:32:56,510 --> 00:32:57,640
They are so precise.

498
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,450
You are obviously not a novice.

499
00:33:00,910 --> 00:33:02,960
You've been with the Gu family for years.

500
00:33:02,960 --> 00:33:03,550
I should

501
00:33:04,110 --> 00:33:05,710
be showing you some respect.

502
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:08,130
But this isn't just any other matter.

503
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,480
Madam has passed away,

504
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:13,060
and the whole family is grieving.

505
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:13,960
Yet you're thinking about

506
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:15,820
siphoning money from the estate.

507
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:17,480
Guards.

508
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:18,450
Drag him out,

509
00:33:18,750 --> 00:33:19,870
give him twenty strokes,

510
00:33:19,870 --> 00:33:20,590
and kick him out!

511
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:20,920
Yes.

512
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:22,720
Spare my life, My Lady!

513
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,490
Forgive me, My Lady!

514
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:25,400
My Lady!

515
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:26,880
My Lady!

516
00:33:28,510 --> 00:33:29,070
Miss Gu.

517
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:31,720
Guard Chen.

518
00:33:32,230 --> 00:33:32,880
Third Master ordered me

519
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:33,830
to send some servants

520
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:34,680
for you to use.

521
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,510
They are all waiting outside.

522
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:37,480
Third Master also said

523
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:39,210
he will come see you a bit later.

524
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:40,840
Thank you.

525
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:57,480
I know.

526
00:33:59,160 --> 00:33:59,750
You think

527
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:01,640
this is my first time
managing the household.

528
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:02,640
And I'm just a girl

529
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:03,790
with a thin skin

530
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:05,200
and easy to bully.

531
00:34:06,900 --> 00:34:08,909
If that's what you think, you're wrong.

532
00:34:08,909 --> 00:34:10,710
Anyone who isn't afraid of death

533
00:34:11,030 --> 00:34:12,090
can come and try me.

534
00:34:12,889 --> 00:34:14,710
And those who don't want to work here

535
00:34:14,710 --> 00:34:16,060
can tell me now.

536
00:34:17,730 --> 00:34:19,060
Forgive us, Miss Gu.

537
00:34:19,090 --> 00:34:20,480
Forgive us, Miss Gu.

538
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:21,920
Forgive us, Miss Gu.

539
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:23,570
Forgive us, Miss Gu.

540
00:34:27,550 --> 00:34:28,030
Thanks.

541
00:34:28,030 --> 00:34:28,940
Let's go.

542
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:29,880
Third Master.

543
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:30,610
You're here.

544
00:34:31,469 --> 00:34:32,530
I'll take my leave.

545
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:33,600
How is she?

546
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:36,400
She seems fine.

547
00:34:36,710 --> 00:34:37,670
Everything is being handled

548
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:38,670
in an orderly way.

549
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:40,630
The more orderly she seems,

550
00:34:40,630 --> 00:34:42,290
the worse she actually feels.

551
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:44,290
Lord Chen, please wait.

552
00:34:49,380 --> 00:34:50,230
The Grand Secretary

553
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:52,760
requests your presence
at Wenyuan Pavilion.

554
00:34:56,980 --> 00:34:58,630
Go fetch me a set of mourning clothes

555
00:34:58,630 --> 00:34:59,430
and wait here.

556
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:00,590
Yes.

557
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:06,280
Master Ye, the heir of Marquis Changxing

558
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:09,210
and the Fifth Madam Gu
are here to pay their respects.

559
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:16,460
Given your status,

560
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,400
a bow is enough.

561
00:37:30,080 --> 00:37:32,210
Did your mother really die of illness?

562
00:37:41,970 --> 00:37:43,710
Why would you say that?

563
00:37:44,810 --> 00:37:45,810
What do you think?

564
00:37:46,150 --> 00:37:46,840
Others may not know,

565
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:47,800
but I do.

566
00:37:49,550 --> 00:37:51,160
Your mother was murdered.

567
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:52,710
Who did it?

568
00:37:53,190 --> 00:37:54,520
I'll help you kill them.

569
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:04,360
Good child.

570
00:38:05,030 --> 00:38:05,940
I heard

571
00:38:05,970 --> 00:38:08,070
you've been handling
all the funeral arrangements.

572
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:09,600
Take good care of yourself.

573
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:11,110
Your mother's spirit in heaven

574
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:11,800
would surely be comforted

575
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,760
to see how filial

576
00:38:13,070 --> 00:38:14,070
you and Rong are.

577
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:16,590
Thank you, Mrs. Gu.

578
00:38:18,230 --> 00:38:19,830
Then we shall take our leave.

579
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:23,520
-Gu Jinzhao.
-Go back first.

580
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,030
Do you have any idea

581
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:32,090
what you're doing?

582
00:38:32,150 --> 00:38:33,690
You, the heir of a marquisate,

583
00:38:33,690 --> 00:38:34,550
were kneeling before the coffin

584
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:35,510
of a commoner woman

585
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:37,190
without even an official title.

586
00:38:37,190 --> 00:38:38,410
With so many eyes watching,

587
00:38:38,410 --> 00:38:40,070
how improper is this conduct!

588
00:38:40,390 --> 00:38:41,390
I truly regret it.

589
00:38:41,550 --> 00:38:43,630
I should never have softened my heart
and brought you here.

590
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:45,430
You're not being soft-hearted.

591
00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:47,710
You just wanted to use this opportunity
to remind me

592
00:38:47,710 --> 00:38:49,440
to give up on Gu Jinzhao.

593
00:38:50,330 --> 00:38:51,460
Even if that's true,

594
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:52,710
I'm doing this for your own good

595
00:38:52,710 --> 00:38:54,040
and for the marquisate.

596
00:38:54,070 --> 00:38:55,710
Do you think I want to be

597
00:38:55,710 --> 00:38:57,110
the one to tear you apart?

598
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,980
If I were a man,

599
00:39:00,100 --> 00:39:01,320
able to establish my own household

600
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,560
and serve the marquisate,

601
00:39:02,560 --> 00:39:04,160
I wouldn't need to force you.

602
00:39:04,230 --> 00:39:06,090
You could marry whoever you want.

603
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,320
But I am not.

604
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:09,880
I can only support my husband

605
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:10,880
and raise my children
in another household,

606
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:13,810
watching our family's future
with growing anxiety.

607
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:47,480
If I had known

608
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,480
you would treat yourself like this,

609
00:39:49,710 --> 00:39:50,710
I should have let you

610
00:39:50,710 --> 00:39:51,550
die back then.

611
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,760
Why did I even bother saving you?

612
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:57,490
Madam Ji didn't die of illness.

613
00:39:58,440 --> 00:39:59,360
Obviously.

614
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,400
I asked Zhao who did it,

615
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:04,270
but she wouldn't say.

616
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:06,110
It's not that she wouldn't say.

617
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,400
She couldn't.

618
00:40:08,190 --> 00:40:08,960
Madam Ji

619
00:40:09,030 --> 00:40:10,560
was probably not murdered.

620
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:12,480
She took her own life.

621
00:40:15,290 --> 00:40:16,410
How do you know?

622
00:40:19,670 --> 00:40:21,320
Didn't I tell you last time?

623
00:40:24,550 --> 00:40:25,550
Madam Ji

624
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,510
suffered from liver qi stagnation

625
00:40:28,510 --> 00:40:31,000
and depression
that developed into illness.

626
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:32,190
For someone like that,

627
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:34,520
if they cannot resolve their inner knots,

628
00:40:34,630 --> 00:40:35,770
it more often than

629
00:40:36,320 --> 00:40:37,450
not ends in suicide.

630
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:40,930
It's just unfortunate for Miss Gu.

631
00:40:41,280 --> 00:40:43,610
She lost her mother before ever marrying.

632
00:40:44,070 --> 00:40:45,400
It's also troublesome.

633
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,280
I will take care of her.

634
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:52,840
I know what you are thinking.

635
00:40:53,110 --> 00:40:54,510
You are overthinking it.

636
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:56,090
You can't take care of her.

637
00:40:56,920 --> 00:40:58,280
Why don't even you believe me?

638
00:40:58,280 --> 00:41:00,140
It's not that I don't believe you.

639
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,280
In this world,

640
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:03,890
if you can't stand on your own feet,

641
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:05,580
you can't take care of anyone.

642
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,840
With your health,

643
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:10,360
no matter how capable I am,

644
00:41:10,670 --> 00:41:11,730
I can't heal you enough

645
00:41:11,730 --> 00:41:13,790
to fight enemies on the battlefield.

646
00:41:14,590 --> 00:41:15,920
If you can't stand firm,

647
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:18,130
this marquisate cannot stand either.

648
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:19,720
If the marquisate falls,

649
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,070
you will have no say

650
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,770
over your own marriage.

651
00:41:24,510 --> 00:41:26,000
This is all fate.

652
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:28,400
Others may believe in fate,

653
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:29,320
but I don't.

654
00:41:30,190 --> 00:41:31,000
Back then, everyone

655
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:32,110
said my heart condition was severe

656
00:41:32,110 --> 00:41:33,550
and I wouldn't live past ten.

657
00:41:33,550 --> 00:41:34,230
But you still saved me,

658
00:41:34,230 --> 00:41:35,190
didn't you?

659
00:41:36,710 --> 00:41:37,720
I don't believe

660
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:40,230
that military merit
is the only way to stand firm.

661
00:41:40,230 --> 00:41:41,230
In this world,

662
00:41:41,590 --> 00:41:42,480
there must be

663
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:44,340
a path other than military merit.

664
00:41:48,530 --> 00:41:52,380
[Harmony Brings Blessings]

665
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:51,070
Upon hearing of Madam Ji's

666
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:52,000
sudden passing,

667
00:41:52,550 --> 00:41:54,150
my mother was deeply grieved

668
00:41:54,150 --> 00:41:55,550
and has specially sent me

669
00:41:55,920 --> 00:41:57,920
to offer condolences on her behalf.

670
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:00,110
The Old Madam truly values old ties.

671
00:42:01,550 --> 00:42:02,190
Lord Chen.

672
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,150
My younger brother

673
00:42:04,150 --> 00:42:05,400
has been struck by sudden misfortune

674
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,630
and is gravely ill and bedridden.

675
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:07,230
Otherwise,

676
00:42:07,230 --> 00:42:08,150
he would definitely have come
to receive you in person.

677
00:42:08,150 --> 00:42:08,840
It's fine.

678
00:43:27,900 --> 00:43:31,240
[A Splendid Match]
